-- Trafigura Said to Hire Standard’s Thomson as Metals Trader
-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 2013-01-30T14:22:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-30/trafigura-said-to-hire-standard-s-thomson-as-metals-trader-1-.html
Trafigura Beheer BV hired Ben Thomson to trade industrial metals, according to two people with
direct knowledge of the matter.  Thomson will be based in  Singapore , said the people, who
asked not to be identified because the information is private.
He previously was head of the physical metals trading desk at
 Standard Bank  Group Ltd. in Singapore, Jim Coupland, Standard
Bank’s global co-head of commodities, said by phone in London
today.  Victoria Dix, a spokeswoman for Trafigura, said the company
doesn’t comment on staff changes.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Agnieszka Troszkiewicz in London at 
